Text: This is episode 9 from season 2 (or episode 22 of 26) that originally aired May 23. A big "THANK YOU" to the uploader for posting this episode.  I've been waiting for this episode for a month.

Yes, it's the 9th show of 2013 and you're welcome.

Did some Google searching and came up with this one and a couple of others before they were posted here by someone else.

Just so we're clear this is actually still First Season. 
There is no "Season 2" yet.  How do I know ?  I just watched the 13th show of 2013 and Kamau Bell said it was the last show of the first year...
